{"tid":1578252,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]cut夜馬根本係政府同馬會聯手做場戲，要醜化示威者","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T15:46:03.000Z","uid":92110,"like":128,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"223ac088a3d21835e712bcb84a6ff3e1fac9b982","tid":1578252,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"攪馬會文宣一出已經大把手足話唔好攪，到12點後主流聲音都係咪攪<br />\n但馬會已經拿拿臨宣佈cut夜馬，班無腦廢中廢老會點諗?<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一定係你班廢青攪出嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n事實上，手足根本乜都冇做，乜都冇講，根本係政府做假風向，扮晒嚇親馬會，就取消夜馬<br />\n成件事，我哋半點反擊能力都冇。<br />\n<br />\n呢個moment，我淨係諗到可以咁，<br />\n做返文宣，貼連儂牆，話示威者無諗過攪馬會，話成件事係政府自編自導自演<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打一齊入嚟傾吓點拆?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e8c960cdf502ceb4ae938def38c325c6f7f0bd","tid":1578252,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7d8aa99055dc2836f9200cd1d692e0d699d0ac6","tid":1578252,"uid":29010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"真 好鬼"},{"pid":"a979bdeabdcdd65d0b92087b93f748acf1ad099f","tid":1578252,"uid":176681,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"e7d8aa99055dc2836f9200cd1d692e0d699d0ac6","tid":1578252,"uid":29010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2