d1ebfb2d196186c64c3eb1d824e8b9da99be7f","tid":1578252,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:03:22.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"ded6d082c8f266191da99e562a5e1b2c6e406408","tid":1578252,"uid":293472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"塞馬場竟然嚴重過塞機場塞黨鐵?<br />\n幫d廢老輸少d多謝我地潻啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7dde2e93c4a75d51e18489dc4b890093943058","tid":1578252,"uid":141057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"唔好理 冷處理"},{"pid":"0339019ebb4d0b018faadd22be9e885fa2ebe7aa","tid":1578252,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a371b608124066cac03263763f6e7aa4a148b1","tid":1578252,"uid":92110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8158e3